  "description": "A stunning nighttime view of a city skyline illuminated with bright lights, punctuated by a vibrant fireworks display. A long bridge stretches across dark water in the foreground, its lights mirroring in the water. The city itself is a mix of modern skyscrapers and older buildings, creating a varied and dynamic skyline. The fireworks burst with blue, white, and red hues, adding a festive and celebratory atmosphere. A green, hilly landscape separates the bridge and the city.",
